{"tid":1492800,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人準備去緬甸？","createTime":"2019-08-21T03:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T05:14:19.000Z","uid":47883,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8975e93862efc369777d3577476372628be858f9","tid":1492800,"uid":47883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:57:49.000Z","msg":"公司要小弟清假 突然有10日假期<br />\n屎忽痕想去緬甸走嗰轉<br />\n有d rush 星期六就出發<br />\n暫時諗住仰光-&gt;蒲甘-&gt;曼德勒<br />\n有冇巴絲都準備去或者有咩建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ab7a65f29db5be7a01ff094b8031f72df84fd5","tid":1492800,"uid":126868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:03:55.000Z","msg":"帶全新美金 100 元鈔票 <br />\n仰光好悶 <br />\n蒲甘玩三日夠 <br />\n有時間可以去埋萊茵湖 <br />\n<br />\n記得帶拖鞋 <br />\n租 e bike 睇下條軚有冇光頭 <br />\n可以帶多幾張$10 港幣 蒲甘個邊d人會友善地問你可否比佢做紀念品"},{"pid":"c42401c0a081873c9b78c26ec8bea86c2277b370","tid":1492800,"uid":191196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:06:44.000Z","msg":"上兩個月去完<br />\n美金一定要直版，唔係佢地唔收<br />\n兌緬紙太爛可以叫佢換，不同版本既美金同金額好似有唔同rate"},{"pid":"cc1d7fd2f75a07b7bd5b9ac0acaa69f68e78374d","tid":1492800,"uid":36207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:39:42.000Z","msg":"蒲甘嘅人好Nice 日出日落都好靚 可以留多幾日<br />\n好多寺同佛塔都要赤腳入去 建議著對舒服啲嘅拖鞋去 方便啲 <br />\n要帶定電筒/頭燈 因為有啲地方有機會停電"},{"pid":"cd214573dd1224605c7fb74140ea690a6b2b13e2","tid":1492800,"uid":47883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:11:31.000Z","msg":"落雨係咪會好麻煩 咩景都睇唔到？"},{"pid":"865a82ca576a3fa035775e4e1caffac36489aa16","tid":1492800,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:18:21.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0452082de299fbf357b82d5ab7a0a440cb57515","tid":1492800,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd214573dd1224605c7fb74140ea690a6b2b13e2","tid":1492800,"uid":47883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1