都至少十個鐘車程<br />\n坐夜巴坐到腳痺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:07:27.000Z","msg":"內陸機又好貴"},{"pid":"f8431de17caad0881837f8706b5d5f2f43ccf3c7","tid":1492800,"uid":122459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:18:44.000Z","msg":"記得離開緬甸前 係入禁區前換番緬甸幣做美金...除非你會再去啦<br />\n<br />\n小心蒲甘D 的士司機....同有班人入寺前會幫你KEEP鞋  但之後會屈你買野...."},{"pid":"d282aba6e891000e9ce12f3d9b63e4b4d1166f8d","tid":1492800,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:55:38.000Z","msg":"需唔需要緬甸幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我用淨左喎"},{"pid":"c485d3b687b49e374876e11f17361025b5959729","tid":1492800,"uid":311247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:36:43.000Z","msg":"蒲甘既人普遍都nice既，不過係佛塔附近撩你話帶你去佢守既佛塔就唔好俾佢呃到，佢地會用呢個藉口之後收你幾十至一百美金做參觀費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n蒲甘日出易睇過日落，果時係蒲甘3日都無成功睇到一次日落...<br />\n曼德勒要去烏本橘同曼德勒山睇日落，有時間係hostel join一日團去敏貢(利申我無去，不過聽係hostel遇到而有去既人都話靚) dl定grab，去到好有用，你唔怕既就用grab叫電單車坐車尾，好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仰光就真係無咩行，都係去下大金塔"},{"pid":"63bf4b3102a80a6fcbb54bbe3188d067425fba0e","tid":1492800,"uid":191196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:57:45.000Z","msg":"仰光每日係有停電的<br />\n分單雙日停唔同時段<br />\n通常大商場冇影響<br />\n但d resort就會冇冷氣冇燈"},{"pid":"93ce04523474a0815f45de842557e3c14db7855d","tid":1492800,"uid":163470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:07:26.000Z","msg":"有時間去埋大金石，唔錯<br />\n但呢一兩年好似開放左大陸免簽，好L多大陸人"},{"pid":"8152da2e3fd5f9220d82b1e216b54d898a74d5cf","tid":1492800,"uid":313475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"係仰光跳火車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行落農田再行返市中心<br />\n<br />\n金塔中午地面熱到煎蛋, 夜晚行好D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245922bea52ce73082373c1de319e9da960a5226","tid":1492800,"uid":40160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3028d7df6e336a8d4813c8dba8e3b33a34197592","tid":1492800,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a2fe5963e6244ca2d99d2de99f4fe946a615ce0","tid":1492800,"uid":47883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"282b4b041f5cccd8382ee1a095f0cf7fe517ae25","tid":1492800,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T07:31:59.000Z","msg":"雨季冇熱氣球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日出fail <br />\n日落都有 但都多雲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T07:42:59.000Z","msg":"咁睇景咪灰濛濛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係呀 返仰光走好似浪費日搭車咁"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T07:47:57.000Z","msg":"多雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係呀 你返仰光都至少十個鐘車程<br />\n坐夜巴坐到腳痺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:47:37.000Z","msg":"梗係坐夜巴 慳番晚住宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5905591d04cab66b6d1c3eda4c50991adb4430f9","tid":1492800,"uid":124245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:17:39.000Z","msg":"需要蒲甘tuk tuk 包車可推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想爬佛塔睇日岀最好有人帶<br />\n去之做下功課<br />\n如果唔係睇十個八個寺睇完都唔知自己睇左乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得最靚係anada<br />\nd 地攤仔唔怕死可以試下 travel like a local 嘛<br />\n利申痾左幾日<br />\n<br />\n漆器workshop 都可以睇下 當開眼界<br />\n前舖後workshop 會有staff 跟但唔會force 你買<br />\n<br />\n宜家唔係雨季咩，入去d 寺勁污糟喎<br />\n高度建議着拖鞋 行完搵濕巾抹下腳就走得<br />\n敏貢一定要去，雖然好遠但我覺得係睇日落最靚"}]}